
tinyfont specification

+------------------+--------------------------------------------------+
| Bytes            | Description                                      |
+------------------+--------------------------------------------------+
| 8                | "tinyfont" magic number                          |
+------------------+--------------------------------------------------+
| 2,n              | length, copyright                                |
+------------------+--------------------------------------------------+
| 2                | em size = ascent + descent                       |
+------------------+--------------------------------------------------+
| 2,{2,2}          | maplength, {codepoint, offset}                   |
+------------------+--------------------------------------------------+
| 2,2,2,{12|12|28} | codepoint, glyphwidth, length, {xym|xyl|xyxyxyc} |
+------------------+--------------------------------------------------+
All values are in big endian, except 'c', 'l', 'm' are LE uint32_t.
Text is in utf-8.
CodePoints are integers in Unicode BMP.
Offset is from end of map.
Point coordinates are in IEEE 754 "Binary32".
Glyphlength is length from start of glyph entry.
